$ Azure Blueprints

*Enabling quick, repeatable creation of governed environments*

Blueprints supports setting up an environment constisting of the following *artifact*:
  • → Microsoft/Azure/resource/group[resource groups]
  • policies
  • role assignments
  • ARM template deployments

Azure Blueprints uses the globally distributed → Microsoft/Azure/products/Cosmos-DB to replicate Blueprint objects to multiple regions.

